00:07:01.504 --> 00:07:04.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>At least, he claims he doesn't.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:07:04.173 --> 00:07:08.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But he does think he can convince them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to surrender without a fight.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:07:08.594 --> 00:07:10.721 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're bringing him along.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:07:10.805 --> 00:07:13.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's also the fact that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he spent time in the Borderland.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:07:13.808 --> 00:07:15.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Borderland?</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:07:15.643 --> 00:07:18.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's the area where</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Klingon ship was attacked.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:07:18.229 --> 00:07:20.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a volatile region</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>between the Klingon empire</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:07:21.023 --> 00:07:23.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and the Orion Syndicate.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:07:23.359 --> 00:07:26.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It attracts the most dangerous</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>elements from both.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:07:26.362 --> 00:07:27.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sorry I asked.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:07:27.905 --> 00:07:31.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Klingons have threatened to retaliate</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with everything they've got.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:07:31.409 --> 00:07:35.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're the fastest ship</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and the most experienced crew.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:07:36.456 --> 00:07:39.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have to find the Augments</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and bring them back.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:07:41.210 --> 00:07:43.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's the only way to avert a war.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:07:45.756 --> 00:07:47.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We launch in six hours.</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:07:51.304 --> 00:07:53.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've mastered their engine controls.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:07:54.056 --> 00:07:57.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wing-mounted disruptor cannons,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>photon torpedo launchers.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:07:57.351 --> 00:07:59.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This ship's an arsenal.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:07:59.479 --> 00:08:01.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're finally free.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:08:08.696 --> 00:08:10.072 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A fine ship.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:08:13.075 --> 00:08:14.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:08:21.709 --> 00:08:23.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I thought you'd be pleased.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:08:23.503 --> 00:08:25.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't sanction this attack.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:08:25.505 --> 00:08:27.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you'd failed,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they would have come after all of us.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:08:27.840 --> 00:08:29.050 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't fail.</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:08:29.133 --> 00:08:30.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Their government knows what we did.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:08:30.760 --> 00:08:32.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They have ships hunting for us right now.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:08:32.762 --> 00:08:34.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They won't find us.</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:08:40.102 --> 00:08:43.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was time for us to leave</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this godforsaken planet.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:08:43.272 --> 00:08:45.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That was my decision, not yours!</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:08:47.109 --> 00:08:49.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you forgotten who I am?</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:08:49.779 --> 00:08:50.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you?</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:08:53.115 --> 00:08:54.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, Raakin.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:08:54.951 --> 00:08:56.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Say it.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:08:57.745 --> 00:08:59.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're our leader.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:09:05.127 --> 00:09:08.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't ever make me ask you again.</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:09:08.297 --> 00:09:10.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Notify me when the rest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of our supplies are on board.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:09:11.509 --> 00:09:13.094 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're leaving orbit.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:09:26.315 --> 00:09:28.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Permission to come aboard, sir?</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:09:30.695 --> 00:09:32.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is my science officer, T'Pol.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:09:32.655 --> 00:09:34.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No need for an introduction.</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:09:34.198 --> 00:09:37.034 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I admire your people very much.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:09:37.118 --> 00:09:39.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We share a similar view of humanity.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:09:39.161 --> 00:09:40.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What view is that?</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:09:40.496 --> 00:09:42.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That it could stand some improvement.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:09:43.082 --> 00:09:46.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I believe that's true of most species,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if not all.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:09:46.794 --> 00:09:47.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckles )</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:09:48.045 --> 00:09:50.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My tactical officer, Lieutenant Reed.</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:09:50.214 --> 00:09:51.257 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:09:51.340 --> 00:09:54.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've heard of you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but I don't recognize your face.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:09:54.427 --> 00:09:56.887 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not getting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your fair share of publicity.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:09:57.471 --> 00:09:59.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think I've had all I can stand.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:09:59.890 --> 00:10:01.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've prepared some quarters.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:10:01.809 --> 00:10:04.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll be under guard at all times.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:10:04.604 --> 00:10:06.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you should decide</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you need to "clear your head."</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:10:07.064 --> 00:10:08.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( scoffs )</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:10:08.316 --> 00:10:10.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're on a starship</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>soon to be at high warp.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:10:10.818 --> 00:10:12.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where exactly would I go?</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:10:13.613 --> 00:10:14.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's this way.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:10:17.033 --> 00:10:19.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I could examine the DNA samples</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Klingons recovered,</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:10:19.535 --> 00:10:22.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could tell you something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about the current state of the Augments.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:10:22.663 --> 00:10:25.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have the information</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sent to your quarters.</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:10:25.166 --> 00:10:28.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A laboratory would be preferable,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your sickbay.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:10:28.461 --> 00:10:31.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dr. Phlox's reputation rivals my own...</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:10:31.297 --> 00:10:32.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Before I was imprisoned, of course.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:10:33.007 --> 00:10:34.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'd enjoy trading notes with him.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:10:34.634 --> 00:10:36.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll consider it.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:10:37.470 --> 00:10:39.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( device humming )</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:10:44.644 --> 00:10:46.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So, how was the honeymoon?</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:10:47.063 --> 00:10:49.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Honeymoon?</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:10:49.231 --> 00:10:51.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You were on Vulcan another</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>two weeks after I left. I figured...</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:10:52.026 --> 00:10:53.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door opens )</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:10:56.405 --> 00:10:57.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:10:57.990 --> 00:11:00.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It comes with everything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but its own protein resequencer.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:11:00.743 --> 00:11:03.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For that, I'll need another day.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:11:10.086 --> 00:11:11.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:11:16.550 --> 00:11:18.260 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I like it.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:11:18.344 --> 00:11:20.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We don't have time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to go over all the details.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:11:20.388 --> 00:11:22.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just, uh, try not to hit that button.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:11:23.933 --> 00:11:25.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're cleared for launch.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:11:32.733 --> 00:11:34.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Here we are again.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:11:41.659 --> 00:11:43.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wouldn't have it any other way.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:11:49.959 --> 00:11:51.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Travis.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:11:55.673 --> 00:11:57.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( energy humming )</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:12:23.909 --> 00:12:27.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just received an intelligence report.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:12:27.455 --> 00:12:30.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A Klingon warship was spotted</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>near Proxima Colony.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:12:30.749 --> 00:12:32.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Admiral Forrest thinks they could be</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:12:32.334 --> 00:12:35.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>conducting reconnaissance</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for a future strike.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:12:36.088 --> 00:12:37.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wanted to keep you up to date.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:12:38.215 --> 00:12:41.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My government is trying</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to work out a diplomatic solution.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:12:41.552 --> 00:12:43.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's still a chance</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they'll be successful.</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:12:44.472 --> 00:12:45.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Small chance.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:12:47.516 --> 00:12:48.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One other thing.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:12:53.689 --> 00:12:57.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's your first official day of duty,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Commander T'Pol.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:13:00.196 --> 00:13:01.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A present.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:13:06.577 --> 00:13:08.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's from the early 20th century.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:13:12.291 --> 00:13:14.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Should help keep you pointed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the right direction.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:13:17.171 --> 00:13:18.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm glad you're with us.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:13:23.636 --> 00:13:25.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:13:27.890 --> 00:13:31.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Captain's starlog, May 17, 2154.</i></c.bg_transparent>

210
00:13:32.061 --> 00:13:33.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We've crossed into the Borderland,</i></c.bg_transparent>

211
00:13:34.063 --> 00:13:37.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>three light-years from where</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>the Klingons were attacked.</i></c.bg_transparent>

212
00:13:37.316 --> 00:13:39.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Still no sign of their ship.</i></c.bg_transparent>

213
00:13:40.277 --> 00:13:43.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Malik. ( laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:13:43.989 --> 00:13:44.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:13:45.074 --> 00:13:47.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was the rebellious one.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:13:47.910 --> 00:13:50.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Reminded me of myself when I was his age.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:13:53.207 --> 00:13:56.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I came to think of them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as my own children.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:13:56.585 --> 00:14:00.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Must have been difficult</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for you to leave them behind.</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:14:00.714 --> 00:14:02.883 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I knew they'd survive.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:14:05.177 --> 00:14:08.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is extremely sophisticated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>work for 20th-century Earth.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:14:09.640 --> 00:14:12.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I made some modifications of my own.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:14:13.018 --> 00:14:15.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, really? What kind of modifications?</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:14:16.021 --> 00:14:17.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Um...</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:14:17.856 --> 00:14:20.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I prefer to let my work speak for itself.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:14:21.694 --> 00:14:22.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think it already has.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:14:24.864 --> 00:14:27.741 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't realize you shared humanity's</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:14:27.825 --> 00:14:31.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>reactionary attitude</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>toward this field of medicine.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:14:32.371 --> 00:14:34.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On the contrary.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:14:34.498 --> 00:14:36.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've used genetic engineering on Denobula</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:14:36.667 --> 00:14:39.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>for over two centuries,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to generally positive effect.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:14:39.295 --> 00:14:41.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you don't approve of what I've done.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:14:41.547 --> 00:14:44.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You tried to redesign your species.</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:14:44.091 --> 00:14:45.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The first time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that was attempted on Earth,</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:14:45.718 --> 00:14:48.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>the result was 30 million deaths.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:14:48.387 --> 00:14:51.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can't let past mistakes hold us back.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:14:51.807 --> 00:14:55.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's your responsibility as a scientist</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to learn from past mistakes.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:14:56.061 --> 00:14:58.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, what makes you think I haven't?</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:14:58.480 --> 00:15:00.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can read.</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:15:07.031 --> 00:15:08.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:15:08.365 --> 00:15:09.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Two vessels are coming up behind us.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:15:09.909 --> 00:15:11.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Orion interceptors.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:15:11.827 --> 00:15:15.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Interesting way of saying hello. Hoshi?</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:15:15.873 --> 00:15:16.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No response.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:15:16.957 --> 00:15:18.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( rumbling )</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:15:33.724 --> 00:15:36.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're getting hammered down here!</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:15:36.310 --> 00:15:38.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Keep firing.</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:15:38.354 --> 00:15:40.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:15:40.272 --> 00:15:42.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm picking up an energy surge</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from one of the interceptors.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:15:42.816 --> 00:15:44.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-A weapon?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No.</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:15:51.158 --> 00:15:52.576 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tucker to the bridge.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:15:52.660 --> 00:15:54.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Two of my people just disappeared.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:15:54.453 --> 00:15:56.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The interceptors have jumped to warp.</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:15:58.999 --> 00:16:00.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're gone.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:16:01.835 --> 00:16:04.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They took nine people, including T'Pol.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:16:04.505 --> 00:16:05.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hmm...</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:16:06.006 --> 00:16:08.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There never used to be</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Orions in this area.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:16:09.009 --> 00:16:12.096 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They must have expanded</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>their range of operations.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:16:12.179 --> 00:16:13.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( clicks tongue )</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:16:13.597 --> 00:16:15.057 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a shame.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:16:15.140 --> 00:16:17.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I really liked your science officer.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:16:17.226 --> 00:16:18.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do I get them back?</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:16:18.602 --> 00:16:20.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs ) It's not going to be easy.</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:16:20.854 --> 00:16:22.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not what I asked you.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:16:23.232 --> 00:16:26.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They've most likely been taken</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to a processing station.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:16:26.402 --> 00:16:28.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The nearest one's on Verex III.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:16:28.362 --> 00:16:29.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( communicator beeps )</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:16:29.488 --> 00:16:31.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Archer to bridge.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Reed.</i></c.bg_transparent>

268
00:16:31.281 --> 00:16:33.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Set a course for Verex III,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>best possible speed.</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:16:33.951 --> 00:16:36.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Yes, sir.</i></c.bg_transparent>

270
00:16:36.245 --> 00:16:37.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What'll happen to them there?</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:16:37.913 --> 00:16:40.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They'll be ushered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>into their new profession...</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:16:40.332 --> 00:16:41.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As slaves.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:16:42.751 --> 00:16:44.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>These stations are heavily guarded.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:16:44.795 --> 00:16:47.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Only legitimate traders</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are permitted to enter.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:16:47.506 --> 00:16:49.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have the feeling you found your way in.</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:16:50.676 --> 00:16:53.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had to establish</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a relationship with the Orions.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:16:53.387 --> 00:16:56.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They helped me acquire</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>certain goods and equipment</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:16:56.682 --> 00:16:59.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I needed to survive.</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:16:59.560 --> 00:17:04.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can get you inside,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but I can't get your people out.</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:17:04.857 --> 00:17:06.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One step at a time.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:17:16.243 --> 00:17:22.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Raakin is taking us to another system</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>where we can live out our lives in peace.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:17:23.959 --> 00:17:26.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I'm sure he's already told you that.</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:17:26.587 --> 00:17:28.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He doesn't tell me everything.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:17:28.547 --> 00:17:30.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This isn't what our father</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>would have wanted.</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:17:31.008 --> 00:17:33.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He didn't raise us to run away and hide.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:17:33.635 --> 00:17:36.180 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, what do you propose?</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:17:36.263 --> 00:17:39.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You could try</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to convince Raakin to reconsider.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:17:39.933 --> 00:17:43.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He only wants one thing from me,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and it isn't advice.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:17:45.898 --> 00:17:47.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It doesn't suit you.</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:17:47.733 --> 00:17:49.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What?</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:17:49.276 --> 00:17:50.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Playing the victim.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:17:58.327 --> 00:18:00.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You chose Raakin.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:18:00.496 --> 00:18:02.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You wanted the strongest for yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:18:04.416 --> 00:18:06.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I still do.</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:18:06.502 --> 00:18:08.003 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:18:08.087 --> 00:18:10.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is it you want?</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:18:13.634 --> 00:18:14.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:18:16.386 --> 00:18:18.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's plenty of time for that.</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:18:24.144 --> 00:18:27.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( electronic humming )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:18:27.106 --> 00:18:30.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You are now the property</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the Orion syndicate.</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:18:30.234 --> 00:18:32.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Break the rules and you will suffer.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:18:33.028 --> 00:18:35.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Follow the rules and you will suffer less.</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:18:35.614 --> 00:18:36.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take her.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:18:36.949 --> 00:18:40.035 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( indistinct shouting )</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:18:56.426 --> 00:18:58.887 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Ensign.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Commander!</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:18:58.971 --> 00:19:00.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you all right?</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:19:00.430 --> 00:19:02.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This thing, it hurts.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:19:02.307 --> 00:19:04.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't touch it.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:19:04.184 --> 00:19:05.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you seen anyone else from the ship?</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:19:05.853 --> 00:19:07.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Just you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-( man screaming )</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:19:07.396 --> 00:19:10.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Where are we?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-An Orion slave market.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:19:10.315 --> 00:19:11.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Slave market?</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:19:11.817 --> 00:19:14.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Orions traffic in forced labor.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:19:14.695 --> 00:19:16.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're being processed for auction.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:19:16.864 --> 00:19:18.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This can't be happening.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:19:18.365 --> 00:19:20.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're gonna come for us, right?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The ship?</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:19:20.826 --> 00:19:21.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ensign--</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:19:21.827 --> 00:19:23.036 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Captain's gonna get us out of here!</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:19:23.120 --> 00:19:24.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ensign!</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:19:26.707 --> 00:19:28.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know your name.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:19:28.208 --> 00:19:31.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pierce. Jeffrey Pierce. I just signed on.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:19:32.004 --> 00:19:33.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jeffrey...</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:19:33.547 --> 00:19:36.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>will come.</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:19:36.592 --> 00:19:39.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It may take some time.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:19:39.261 --> 00:19:42.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We should try to stay together</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>until they get here.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:19:42.222 --> 00:19:43.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sobs )</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:19:49.646 --> 00:19:51.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALE: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Transmit your identification code.</i></c.bg_transparent>

328
00:19:51.648 --> 00:19:53.901 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:19:55.194 --> 00:19:57.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Soong hasn't used this code in years.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:19:57.988 --> 00:20:00.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Give it time.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:20:02.242 --> 00:20:03.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALE: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>You're cleared to proceed.</i></c.bg_transparent>

332
00:20:07.289 --> 00:20:08.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: Phlox.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:20:10.626 --> 00:20:13.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Transponder.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It has a range of 10 kilometers.</c.bg_transparent>

334
