445
00:27:03.121 --> 00:27:05.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckles ) They were more like subjects.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:27:05.623 --> 00:27:08.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh. They were just treated like slaves.</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:27:09.502 --> 00:27:11.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:27:11.796 --> 00:27:14.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'Pol could be shipped out any second.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:27:14.507 --> 00:27:15.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Work fast.</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:27:17.802 --> 00:27:20.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I told him everything.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:27:20.638 --> 00:27:23.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He thinks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you're planning an attack against him.</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:27:23.183 --> 00:27:24.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is he going to move against me?</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:27:24.684 --> 00:27:25.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>See for yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:27:27.604 --> 00:27:29.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is this the move you expected?</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:27:30.982 --> 00:27:32.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's between us.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:27:33.526 --> 00:27:36.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I saved your life once</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when we were children,</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:27:36.488 --> 00:27:38.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>pulled you from the river</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when you fell in.</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:27:38.490 --> 00:27:39.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I remember.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:27:39.866 --> 00:27:42.577 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, 10 years later,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you're plotting against me.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:27:42.660 --> 00:27:45.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm the strongest... and the smartest.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:27:45.705 --> 00:27:48.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doesn't look that way from here.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:27:48.500 --> 00:27:51.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You would never have trapped me like this.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:27:51.461 --> 00:27:52.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gun clicks )</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:27:53.046 --> 00:27:54.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But I have.</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:27:58.885 --> 00:28:00.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry, Raakin.</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:28:00.553 --> 00:28:02.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:28:03.348 --> 00:28:05.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's between us.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:28:05.558 --> 00:28:06.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Saul...</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:28:08.853 --> 00:28:11.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jaya, listen to me.</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:28:11.189 --> 00:28:14.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They only listen to me now.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:28:29.290 --> 00:28:33.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was a time when I looked up to you,</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:28:35.296 --> 00:28:37.549 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>when I called you my brother.</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:28:38.341 --> 00:28:40.093 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am your brother.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:28:40.176 --> 00:28:45.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When you rejected our father's wishes,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you stopped being one of us.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:28:45.890 --> 00:28:48.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And when that happened...</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:28:48.685 --> 00:28:50.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You ceased to exist.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:28:52.147 --> 00:28:54.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( blade plunges )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:28:54.315 --> 00:28:56.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groans )</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:28:58.069 --> 00:29:00.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Which makes this an act of mercy.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:29:04.659 --> 00:29:06.035 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get rid of him.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:29:12.792 --> 00:29:13.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:29:16.504 --> 00:29:18.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not for him.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:29:21.092 --> 00:29:22.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>TUCKER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>We're sending the code now.</i></c.bg_transparent>

484
00:29:23.011 --> 00:29:24.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeps )</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:29:24.512 --> 00:29:25.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Got it.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:29:37.442 --> 00:29:38.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( hypospray hisses )</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:29:38.568 --> 00:29:40.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasping )</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:29:58.880 --> 00:29:59.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:30:04.093 --> 00:30:06.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( indistinct conversations )</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:30:10.600 --> 00:30:11.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Outside.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:30:14.813 --> 00:30:16.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Outside.</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:30:24.072 --> 00:30:27.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( speaking indistinctly )</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:30:27.116 --> 00:30:29.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:30:29.202 --> 00:30:30.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( device deactivates )</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:30:34.457 --> 00:30:36.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:30:36.292 --> 00:30:37.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:30:37.418 --> 00:30:40.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The restraints are off!</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:30:40.380 --> 00:30:42.632 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( indistinct shouting )</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:30:45.218 --> 00:30:48.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Slaves are loose! Slaves are loose!</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:30:49.055 --> 00:30:51.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( alarm blaring )</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:31:02.485 --> 00:31:03.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groans )</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:31:03.862 --> 00:31:06.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Trip, start beaming them, five at a time.</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:31:06.239 --> 00:31:07.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( zaps )</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:31:10.827 --> 00:31:13.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sorry, Captain. Hope you find your people.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:31:13.454 --> 00:31:14.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks for the ride.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:31:22.255 --> 00:31:23.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:31:24.883 --> 00:31:26.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've got spirit.</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:31:26.259 --> 00:31:28.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I might just keep you for myself.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:31:29.137 --> 00:31:30.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:31:30.722 --> 00:31:32.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not for sale.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:31:36.811 --> 00:31:38.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Trip, have you got everyone?</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:31:38.897 --> 00:31:40.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You and Soong are the only ones left.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:31:40.815 --> 00:31:43.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Soong got away.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Locate him and beam him up.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:31:46.070 --> 00:31:47.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:31:47.447 --> 00:31:48.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( zaps )</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:31:48.531 --> 00:31:51.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:31:52.160 --> 00:31:53.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( screaming )</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:31:59.792 --> 00:32:02.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Soong's transponder signal, it's dead.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:32:02.128 --> 00:32:04.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can you scan for his bio-sign?</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:32:04.255 --> 00:32:06.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're trying,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but there's too many people down there.</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:32:06.424 --> 00:32:08.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( indistinct shouting )</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:32:38.414 --> 00:32:39.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:32:39.874 --> 00:32:42.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:32:46.089 --> 00:32:47.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:32:47.840 --> 00:32:49.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALE: Help me!</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:32:49.509 --> 00:32:51.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:32:51.803 --> 00:32:53.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't let them take me!</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:33:07.026 --> 00:33:08.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:33:14.450 --> 00:33:15.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:33:15.952 --> 00:33:17.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( exclaims )</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:33:19.664 --> 00:33:20.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( communicator beeps )</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:33:20.999 --> 00:33:23.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Trip, two to beam up.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:33:34.012 --> 00:33:36.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: You knew exactly where</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Orions were operating.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:33:36.806 --> 00:33:38.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You knew they'd abduct members of my crew.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:33:38.850 --> 00:33:42.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe you were even hoping they'd get you.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:33:42.437 --> 00:33:44.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was an outside chance.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:33:44.147 --> 00:33:47.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You were determined to escape,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>no matter who got hurt.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:33:47.108 --> 00:33:48.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No one was injured.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:33:48.401 --> 00:33:51.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nine of my people were</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>nearly sold into slavery.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:33:51.446 --> 00:33:53.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Two of them may have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>permanent physical damage</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:33:53.906 --> 00:33:55.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>because of the restraints.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:33:55.116 --> 00:33:57.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't take this action lightly.</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:33:57.243 --> 00:33:59.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that supposed to justify what you did?</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:33:59.203 --> 00:34:04.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm simply saying it wasn't easy for me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to place you and your crew in jeopardy.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:34:06.335 --> 00:34:08.171 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I respect you, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:34:08.921 --> 00:34:10.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then tell me how to find the Augments.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:34:12.592 --> 00:34:14.719 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know where they're going.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:34:14.802 --> 00:34:18.347 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They didn't steal a Klingon ship</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to go sightseeing.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:34:18.431 --> 00:34:19.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're dangerous.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:34:19.599 --> 00:34:21.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're the future.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:34:21.350 --> 00:34:25.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're stronger, smarter,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>free from sickness,</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:34:25.605 --> 00:34:28.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>with lifespans twice as long as our own.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:34:28.775 --> 00:34:30.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:34:30.568 --> 00:34:33.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You, more than anyone,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>should appreciate what this means.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:34:33.821 --> 00:34:34.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why me?</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:34:35.740 --> 00:34:36.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your father...</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:34:36.949 --> 00:34:39.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>suffered from Clarke's Disease.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:34:39.327 --> 00:34:43.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>His final years were marked</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with extreme pain.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:34:43.122 --> 00:34:45.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My father has nothing to do with this.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:34:45.166 --> 00:34:47.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He didn't need to suffer.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:34:47.376 --> 00:34:49.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Genetic engineering could have cured him.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:34:49.921 --> 00:34:51.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Those who want to suppress my Augments</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:34:51.964 --> 00:34:56.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>are the same ones who condemned</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your father to death.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:34:56.385 --> 00:35:00.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Turn the ship around, Captain. Go home.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:35:00.473 --> 00:35:02.642 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Leave them alone.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:35:05.394 --> 00:35:08.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm gonna find them, Doctor...</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:35:08.106 --> 00:35:09.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Whether you help me or not.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:35:11.901 --> 00:35:14.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door opens )</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:35:28.417 --> 00:35:30.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're supposed to be resting.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:35:30.711 --> 00:35:33.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dr. Phlox says I can resume</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my duties this afternoon.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:35:33.548 --> 00:35:35.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm glad they got that thing off</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with no problem.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:35:36.342 --> 00:35:39.053 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's a slight ringing in my left ear,</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:35:39.137 --> 00:35:41.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but it should dissipate over time.</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:35:41.597 --> 00:35:43.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:35:45.268 --> 00:35:47.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I'll let you get back to that.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:35:49.021 --> 00:35:52.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vulcans don't have honeymoons.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:35:52.650 --> 00:35:57.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After the ceremony,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I went to Mount Seleya to meditate...</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:35:57.238 --> 00:35:58.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( clears throat )</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:35:58.322 --> 00:35:59.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Alone.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:36:00.908 --> 00:36:03.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's none of my business, anyway.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:36:03.452 --> 00:36:05.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( explosions )</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:36:05.705 --> 00:36:08.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Orion interceptors, two of them,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>coming up fast.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:36:08.499 --> 00:36:10.585 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-They're hailing us.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:36:10.668 --> 00:36:12.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is Captain Archer of the starship--</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:36:12.128 --> 00:36:13.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALE: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>You've stolen our property.</i></c.bg_transparent>

586
00:36:13.838 --> 00:36:16.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They were members of my crew.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You kidnapped them.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:36:16.883 --> 00:36:20.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Disengage your warp drive</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>and deactivate your weapons.</i></c.bg_transparent>

588
00:36:20.469 --> 00:36:22.221 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That isn't going to happen.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:36:24.599 --> 00:36:25.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Malcolm.</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:36:33.482 --> 00:36:35.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're targeting our Nacelles.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:36:35.484 --> 00:36:37.236 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're dropping out of warp.</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:36:37.320 --> 00:36:38.571 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Torpedoes.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:36:41.449 --> 00:36:42.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's another ship.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:36:55.296 --> 00:36:57.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The second Orion's veering off.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They're retreating.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:36:57.924 --> 00:36:59.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:36:59.175 --> 00:37:00.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Klingons are requesting to dock.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:37:13.439 --> 00:37:16.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know he's on this ship.</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:37:16.108 --> 00:37:18.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We received his signal.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:37:18.277 --> 00:37:22.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When he tried to escape,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I saw him access a console.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:37:22.323 --> 00:37:24.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You were expecting us.</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:37:24.951 --> 00:37:26.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where is he?</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:37:26.577 --> 00:37:27.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In the brig.</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:37:27.954 --> 00:37:31.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In a prison cell.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I want to speak with him.</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:37:31.249 --> 00:37:32.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't allow that.</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:37:32.541 --> 00:37:33.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We saved your ship.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:37:34.043 --> 00:37:37.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My ship wouldn't have been in danger</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if we hadn't come looking for you.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:37:40.549 --> 00:37:42.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is it you want with us?</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:37:42.301 --> 00:37:44.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My orders are to take you back to Earth.</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:37:45.263 --> 00:37:46.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Earth...</c.bg_transparent>

610
00:37:46.931 --> 00:37:49.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Considers my father a criminal.</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:37:49.225 --> 00:37:50.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:37:51.060 --> 00:37:52.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because he brought us to life.</c.bg_transparent>

613
00:37:52.561 --> 00:37:56.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You want to take us back to a world</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that opposes our very existence.</c.bg_transparent>

614
00:37:56.482 --> 00:37:58.609 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You attacked a Klingon vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

615
00:37:58.693 --> 00:38:00.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're threatening war.</c.bg_transparent>

616
00:38:00.278 --> 00:38:01.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not our problem.</c.bg_transparent>

617
00:38:03.739 --> 00:38:07.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We don't care what happens to you.</c.bg_transparent>

618
00:38:08.786 --> 00:38:10.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Humanity is no longer relevant.</c.bg_transparent>

619
00:38:11.205 --> 00:38:15.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To quote one of your philosophers...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Nietzsche...</c.bg_transparent>

620
00:38:17.044 --> 00:38:20.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Mankind is something to be surpassed."</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:38:23.092 --> 00:38:25.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You think he was talking about you?</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:38:30.433 --> 00:38:32.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm about to attack you.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:38:33.477 --> 00:38:34.979 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You see?</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:38:35.062 --> 00:38:38.107 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Even with a warning,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you're not fast enough.</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:38:38.190 --> 00:38:39.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let him go.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:38:39.442 --> 00:38:42.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have five times your strength,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>double your intelligence.</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:38:42.862 --> 00:38:43.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let him go!</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:38:43.946 --> 00:38:45.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll tear out his throat!</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:38:47.658 --> 00:38:49.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lower your weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:38:52.288 --> 00:38:53.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:39:02.590 --> 00:39:04.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Persis.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:39:04.091 --> 00:39:06.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've broken their security code,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we're ready.</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:39:09.055 --> 00:39:10.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door opens )</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:39:20.775 --> 00:39:22.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll kill him!</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:39:31.869 --> 00:39:33.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door opens )</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:39:33.704 --> 00:39:35.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:39:48.511 --> 00:39:49.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Persis.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:39:50.471 --> 00:39:51.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Persis?</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:39:53.974 --> 00:39:55.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't believe it.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:39:56.060 --> 00:39:57.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:40:03.818 --> 00:40:05.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Father, here's Malik.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:40:07.738 --> 00:40:08.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Malik.</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:40:10.074 --> 00:40:11.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:40:17.748 --> 00:40:19.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I knew we'd see each other again.</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:40:20.292 --> 00:40:22.044 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm proud of you.</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:40:23.295 --> 00:40:24.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of all of you.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:40:25.214 --> 00:40:27.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Soong, listen to me.</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:40:28.008 --> 00:40:29.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's nothing to say, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:40:29.635 --> 00:40:31.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What should we do with them?</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:40:31.929 --> 00:40:33.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let them go.</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:40:33.514 --> 00:40:35.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But they'll just come after us.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:40:35.474 --> 00:40:37.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Their ship's disabled.</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:40:37.268 --> 00:40:41.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>By the time it's repaired,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we'll be far away.</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:40:41.188 --> 00:40:42.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's been a pleasure, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:40:45.860 --> 00:40:47.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take my advice.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:40:47.820 --> 00:40:50.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go home and start learning</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how to speak Klingon.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:41:11.927 --> 00:41:15.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There were times, back on Earth,</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:41:15.639 --> 00:41:18.559 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>when I doubted myself,</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:41:18.642 --> 00:41:20.060 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>my work.</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:41:21.562 --> 00:41:24.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But seeing you all,</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:41:24.732 --> 00:41:27.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know that everything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I've fought for was worth it.</c.bg_transparent>

662
00:41:28.819 --> 00:41:31.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're going to build a new world.</c.bg_transparent>

663
00:41:31.489 --> 00:41:35.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But we can't begin that task just yet.</c.bg_transparent>

664
00:41:35.159 --> 00:41:38.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thousands of your brothers and sisters</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are waiting to be born.</c.bg_transparent>

665
00:41:42.833 --> 00:41:44.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's go get them.</c.bg_transparent>

